      right: ["Uncontrolled bleeding from multiple sites simultaneously", "Oozing from IV sites, surgical wounds, and mucous membranes", "Petechiae, purpura, ecchymosis spreading", "Organ ischemia from microvascular thrombosis: AKI, hepatic dysfunction, ARDS", "Hemorrhagic stroke"]
